40:15.710 --> 40:17.396
These seats next to you taken?

40:17.843 --> 40:19.472
Nope, they're free.

40:22.342 --> 40:23.763
Oh, taken!

40:23.788 --> 40:25.994
They're taken. Sorry.

40:26.779 --> 40:28.145
You're here.

40:28.180 --> 40:29.947
Of course we are.

40:29.982 --> 40:32.616
