Karen, I'm so sorry. I
handled everything wrong.

40:39.592 --> 40:41.058
It's okay.

40:41.093 --> 40:42.534
I just... it's been really hard the last...

40:42.559 --> 40:43.762
I know.

40:45.221 --> 40:48.362
You are in our life forever, lady, okay?

40:48.398 --> 40:51.165
- Promise me?
- Promise.

40:51.201 --> 40:52.693
Love you.

40:53.870 --> 40:55.803
