40:55.839 --> 40:58.339
Man, this place is <i>
packed.</i> Who's the opening act?

40:59.235 --> 41:01.368
I'm obviously kidding.

41:03.717 --> 41:05.154
Joss.

41:05.179 --> 41:07.365
If this is replacing brunch, I'm eating.

41:07.390 --> 41:08.556
What?!

41:08.767 --> 41:10.711
It's church's chicken!

41:10.736 --> 41:12.302
Put that away. Away!

41:12.327 --> 41:13.627
