41:16.166 --> 41:18.867
Man: Father, son, and the holy spirit.

41:18.892 --> 41:21.059
- No food in church?
- Amen.

41:21.084 --> 41:24.485
♪ There is a way to be
yourself, I assure you this ♪

41:25.219 --> 41:27.354
Sex with a Tucson bartender?

41:29.808 --> 41:31.554
